\end_inset

 
\begin_inset Formula $x\succsim y\overset{f\ represents\ \succsim}{\iff}f\left(x\right)\geq f\left(y\right)\overset{\varphi\ strictly\ increasing}{\iff}\varphi\left(f\left(x\right)\right)\geq\varphi\left(f\left(y\right)\right)\overset{definition\ of\ g}{\iff}g\left(x\right)\geq g\left(y\right)$
